      • RiskAnalyzedTrade

        public RiskAnalyzedTrade​(CryptoTrade originalTrade,
                         Long analysisTimestamp,
                         Double riskScore,
                         RiskLevel finalRiskLevel,
                         List<CharSequence> triggeredPatterns,
                         VolumeAnalysis volumeAnalysis,
                         BehavioralAnalysis behavioralAnalysis,
                         MarketImpactAnalysis marketImpactAnalysis,
                         UserTradingProfile userRiskProfile,
                         List<ComplianceFlag> complianceFlags,
                         List<RiskMitigationAction> riskMitigationActions,
                         AnalyticsMetadata analyticsMetadata,
                         Map<CharSequence,​CharSequence> additionalContext)
        All-args constructor.
        Parameters:
        originalTrade - The original trade event that was analyzed
        analysisTimestamp - When the risk analysis was performed (milliseconds since epoch)
        riskScore - Overall risk score from 0.0 (no risk) to 1.0 (maximum risk)
        finalRiskLevel - Final risk level after CEP analysis
        triggeredPatterns - List of risk patterns that this trade triggered
        volumeAnalysis - Volume-based risk analysis
        behavioralAnalysis - Behavioral pattern analysis
        marketImpactAnalysis - Market impact analysis
        userRiskProfile - User risk profile at time of analysis
        complianceFlags - Compliance and regulatory flags
        riskMitigationActions - Risk mitigation actions taken or recommended
        analyticsMetadata - Analytics processing metadata
        additionalContext - Additional context-specific data
